videos.description: Jase Febres fakes the 3-pointer, then the pass on the drive to get the bucket on a nice lay-in.
videos.headline: Febres fakes and scores

videos.description: Matt Coleman III drives and tosses it up to Jaxson Hayes who gets air and throws down the alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Hayes throws down the hammer

videos.description: Matt Coleman III gets the ball, dribbles and dances to burn clock and then hits the crushing corner 3 to extend Texas' lead late.
videos.headline: Coleman dances and nails the corner 3
